Agent_K http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Agent_K 0 Agent K (born Kevin "Kay" Brown) is a character in the Men in Black franchise. Kay is portrayed by Tommy Lee Jones in the three films and voiced by Ed O'Ross and Gregg Berger in the animated series. The film's trading card series and Men in Black: The Game give K's full name as Kevin Cunningham, a nod to Lowell Cunningham, the creator of the comic.
